officials, establish a comprehensive national database, either within 
or  separate  from  the  Consumer  Sentinel  Network,  that  tracks 
instances of scams related to COVID19. 

(c)  COMMISSION DEFINED.In  this  section,  the  term  Commis-

sion means the Federal Trade Commission. 
SEC. 3. DETERMINATION OF BUDGETARY EFFECTS. 

The budgetary effects of this Act, for the purpose of complying 
with the Statutory Pay-As-You-Go Act of 2010, shall be determined 
by  reference  to  the  latest  statement  titled  Budgetary  Effects  of 
PAYGO  Legislation  for  this  Act,  submitted  for  printing  in  the 
Congressional  Record  by  the  Chairman  of  the  House  Budget  Com-
mittee,  provided  that  such  statement  has  been  submitted  prior 
to the vote on passage. 

Approved January 5, 2021. 

